@sgillies I couldn't find anything specific. I think `meta` makes more sense because it's extensible. For example, for this EWKT/EWKB feature, for `M` type geometries there would need to be some indicator. For example:

```json
{
  "type": "Point",
  "coordinates": [-44.3, 60.1, 100.0],
  "meta": {
    "srid": "4326",
    "components": "XYM" 
  }
}
